title: JimBob One Million
author: VD
content_html:
Congratulations to Made By JimBob, whose SAVAGE MEMES hit one million views on Arktoons yesterday. He’s the complete creator, not only producing great content with one of the most popular comics on the site, but he even assists with Arkhaven’s marketing plans.
